OL,3,C#50bn more public spending needed each
OL,4,Cyear for long-term growth ` think tank
OL,6,FSpending must rise sharply under the
OL,7,Fnew Government to bring UK public
OL,8,Fservices "up to scratch", according to
OL,9,Fa leading think tank.
OL,11,FThe National Institute of Economic and
OL,12,FSocial Research (NIESR) said an extra
OL,13,F#50 billion a year is needed for
OL,14,Fpublic investment to secure long-term
OL,15,Feconomic prosperity.
OL,17,FThis would see public investment rise
OL,18,Ffrom its current level of around 2.5%
OL,19,Fof UK GDP (gross domestic product) to
OL,20,Faround 5% of GDP.
