OL,6,FStephen Millard, deputy director for
OL,7,Fmacroeconomic modelling and
OL,8,Fforecasting at NIESR, said, however,
OL,9,Fthat this would require "either higher
OL,10,Ftaxes or higher borrowing or both".
OL,12,FLast week, Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,13,Findicated that taxes are likely to be
OL,14,Fraised in the autumn Budget after she
OL,15,Fcriticised the state of public
OL,16,Ffinances left by the previous
OL,17,Fgovernment.
