OL,6,FMs Reeves said Labour would stick to
OL,7,Fits election manifesto promises not to
OL,8,Fraise national insurance, income tax
OL,9,For VAT, but left open the possibility
OL,10,Ffor other tax hikes at the Budget on
OL,11,FOctober 30.
OL,13,FThe admission came after she scrapped
OL,14,Fa series of infrastructure projects as
OL,15,Fpart of measures aimed at filling a
OL,16,F#22 billion black hole in the public
OL,17,Ffinances.
