OL,6,FHowever, NIESR stressed the importance
OL,7,Fof public investment in areas such as
OL,8,Ftransport connectivity in order to
OL,9,Fhelp drive economic growth.
OL,11,FThe think tank said the new Government
OL,12,Fwill need to address "low-trend
OL,13,Fproductivity growth, make changes to
OL,14,Fthe current fiscal framework and
OL,15,Fimprove declining living standards".
OL,17,FMr Millard said: "The new Government
OL,18,Fhas inherited an economy with low
OL,19,Finvestment and low productivity
OL,20,Fgrowth, and it is these issues that
OL,21,Fneed to be tackled.
