OL,6,F"In addition, public spending needs to
OL,7,Frise if public services are to be
OL,8,Fbrought up to scratch, the nations and
OL,9,Fregions of the United Kingdom outside
OL,10,FLondon and the South East are to see
OL,11,Fthe regeneration they need, and the
OL,12,Fgovernment is to meet the mandated
OL,13,Ftarget of achieving net zero by 2050."
OL,15,FThe think tank's latest outlook report
OL,16,Fpredicted that output will grow by
OL,17,Faround 1.2% per year over the life of
OL,18,Fthe current Parliament, while
OL,19,Funemployment is likely to remain
OL,20,Faround 4.5%.
