OL,6,FIt also predicted that inflation will
OL,7,Ftick higher again over the second half
OL,8,Fof 2024 and start of 2025 but will
OL,9,Freturn to around the 2% target rate in
OL,10,Fthe medium term.
OL,12,FAdrian Pabst, deputy director for
OL,13,Fpublic policy at NIESR, said: "The
OL,14,FGovernment's mission-driven approach
OL,15,Fand the creation of an Industrial
OL,16,FStrategy Council have the potential to
OL,17,Fovercome barriers to better economic
OL,18,Fpolicy-making such as policy and
OL,19,Fministerial churn, departmental silos
OL,20,Fand a lack of co-ordination across
OL,21,FWhitehall.
